355
00:25:53,467 --> 00:25:54,633
At a certain point,

356
00:25:55,367 --> 00:25:57,300
it doesn't matter how you feel.

357
00:25:58,533 --> 00:25:59,834
Wait.

358
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:02,834
Why wouldn't your emotions be important?

359
00:26:03,433 --> 00:26:05,266
