426
00:31:47,066 --> 00:31:48,767
Se-yeon, where are we?

427
00:31:49,333 --> 00:31:50,333
Come in.

428
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,633
Welcome. It's your first time here, right?

429
00:32:00,900 --> 00:32:03,900
